1:39:10.736 --> 1:39:12.571
Listened to the demo?

1:39:13.197 --> 1:39:15.449
Yeah, it could use some more work...

1:39:15.575 --> 1:39:17.159
What do you know?

1:39:17.285 --> 1:39:20.954
It's brilliant! Shut up, you.
It's the best!

1:39:21.289 --> 1:39:23.206
No fighting.

1:39:36.762 --> 1:39:41.308
